---
import Legal from '../layouts/Legal.astro';
import { social } from '../data/site';
const email = social.email || 'hello@jaindisha.in';
---

<Legal
  title="Contact"
  updated="10 June 2026"
  description="How to reach Disha Jain for counselling, mentoring, bookings and any questions."
>
  <p>
    The easiest way to start is to book a session from the site. For anything else, here is how to
    reach me.
  </p>

  <h2>Email</h2>
  <p>
    <a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a>. I usually reply within one to two working days.
  </p>

  <h2>How sessions happen</h2>
  <p>
    All sessions are <strong>online, over video on Google Meet</strong>. I don't offer in-person or
    walk-in sessions, so you can join from wherever feels safe and comfortable.
  </p>

  <h2>Find me elsewhere</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><a href={social.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
  </ul>

  <p class="note crisis">
    <strong>In a crisis?</strong> I am not an emergency service. If you or someone else is in
    danger, call <strong>112</strong>, or the Tele-MANAS mental health helpline on
    <strong>14416</strong> (toll-free, in India).
  </p>
</Legal>
